        "title": "Forward-port Tideclaw alpha release fixes",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nForward-ports the real fixes from the Tideclaw `v2026.5.28-alpha.1` release branch back to `main`, excluding the alpha version-prep commit.\n\nIncludes fixes for:\n- release workflow alpha/publish proof handling and release-gate stability\n- package tarball production import coverage and private SDK helper exclusions\n- install-smoke/onboard Docker lanes for config-only channels, Gateway auth fallback, and mock OpenAI runtime routing\n- shrinkwrap patch drift handling and related script tests\n- iMessage, QA Lab, kitchen-sink, and plugin discovery test stability\n- macOS CI Node toolcache fallback under `set -u`\n- Plugin SDK API baseline refresh from the release branch\n\n## Verification\n\nBehavior addressed: Tideclaw alpha release fixes are preserved on a forward-port branch without carrying the alpha version bump into `main`.\n\nReal environment tested: Local Codex worktree plus GitHub Actions release gates on the alpha branch.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`; `bash -n .github/actions/setup-pnpm-store-cache/ensure-node.sh`; `bash -uc 'source .github/actions/setup-pnpm-store-cache/ensure-node.sh; RUNNER_TOOL_CACHE=/nope AGENT_TOOLSDIRECTORY=/nope ACTIONS_RUNNER_TOOL_CACHE=/nope OPENCLAW_CONTAINER_TOOL_CACHE=/nope openclaw_find_toolcache_node 24.x >/tmp/node-toolcache.out || status=$?; test \"${status:-0}\" = 1'`; `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs test/scripts/bundled-plugin-build-entries.test.ts test/scripts/generate-npm-shrinkwrap.test.ts test/scripts/docker-build-helper.test.ts src/commands/agents.delete.test.ts extensions/imessage/src/monitor.media-policy.test.ts extensions/imessage/src/send.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/suite-runtime-gateway.test.ts test/scripts/kitchen-sink-rpc-walk.test.ts src/plugins/discovery.test.ts -- --reporter=verbose`.\n\nEvidence after fix: Alpha branch SHA `b6f260b50d` passed CI `26592394994`, Plugin Prerelease `26592394683`, NPM preflight `26592077287`, Release Checks `26592395569`, and Full Release Validation `26592075834` before tagging `v2026.5.28-alpha.1`. The forward-port branch was rebased onto current `origin/main`; the focused local proof passed after rebase; the macOS Node setup failure was patched with a local nounset/no-toolcache probe.\n\nObserved result after fix: `git diff --check` passed; shell syntax/probe passed; focused Vitest passed with 9 files and 242 tests.\n\nWhat was not tested: The latest PR CI rerun is still pending after the rebase and macOS setup fix. Auto Review did not run because the helper could not find a local `codex` binary in this environment.\n",
